{"tid":789763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[柒過關家姐]中國動員堵小英 NASA科學家爆料：抗議還跑錯地方","createTime":"2018-08-22T13:01:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T23:47:46.000Z","uid":20058,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"76c3b05b4a823fc2f36a88aed693b2cbd1a23a4d","tid":789763,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:01:54.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕蔡英文總統訪美期間，進入美國國家航空暨太空總署（NASA）詹森太空中心參訪，被視為突破台美政治進展，NASA太空食物研究室主任郭正光爆料，當天聽聞中國官方欲動員4輛遊覽車前往抗議，結果只有不到10名成年人到場，還因中國官方稱小英進入的地方買票就可進去，而錯跑去「太空遊樂中心」堵人落空。<br />\n請繼續往下閱讀...<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">郭正光在國民黨新北市議員參選人陳偉杰臉書中指出，中國官方似乎為抗議蔡英文進入NASA，原預計動員4部遊覽車的人力前往抗議，但「大概是走路工太低吧」，因此最後取消遊覽車抗議活動，採民眾自發性前往，最後連同5名孩童在內，只有到場將10幾人吆喝、舉看板，場面相當淒涼。<br />\n「他們以為總統要去那個買票就可以進去的太空遊樂中心！」郭正光提供照片並指出，身穿橘色衣服的中國抗議團疑似聽信中國媒體的說法，認為小英不可能去真正的太空中心，因此一群人「空等了1個鐘頭」；郭正光寫到這裡還忍不住「哈哈」冷笑兩聲。<br />\n</span><br />\n蔡英文總統出訪過境美國期間，參訪美國國家航空暨太空總署（NASA）詹森太空中心，被視為具有相當政治意義，但國民黨新北市議員參選人陳偉杰在臉書堅稱，根據友人比對，蔡英文參觀的其實是「太空博物館」，買票就能進入；NASA太空食物研究室主任郭正光留言打臉，強調控制中心非工作人員絕對進不去，連他在NASA工作30多年也只進過一次，直批陳偉杰「真是白痴無腦到極點」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2527751\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2527751&d=rFH6k9xzrxatpSseUVyNPhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=e0725fed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2527751&h=91372a07\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2527751</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8593e4a8ef869b03b864e0cee74f92e0619a921d","tid":789763,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T22:09:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7fa757f89144d27291ea893fc1f2d3048035609","tid":789763,"uid":6192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T22:40:23.000Z","msg":"媽呀 好柒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c765af3f7e57d2ae497e803965a7b0910f99dd2","tid":789763,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T23:00:56.000Z","msg":"國民黨籍議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc1855f64ef46fbc272270b29b6bef41c1dbde98","tid":789763,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T23:10:22.000Z","msg":"KMT<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f28c262e6730f3bdaeea673abe4217807df693","tid":789763,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T23:17:32.000Z","msg":"一D都唔專業"},{"pid":"13c47a673baa61349caee9941ffe8de35a9985bf","tid":789763,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T23:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7ecc67245fdd348e70c16ea4503210f941a53d","tid":789763,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T23:31:33.000Z","msg":"2邊都柒<br />\n打和啦"},{"pid":"7483a3c8b978df69fc75e3bfa0c5e103817c70fa","tid":789763,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T23:35:44.000Z","msg":"哈哈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672a39cccc9a46b1d7b23e78029b2cf882db1e1c","tid":789763,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T23:47:46.000Z","msg":"台灣有美日免簽證<br />\n你嗰d濕鳩邦交 繼續俾錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}